[[科幻|科幻]][[劇情片|剧情]][[网络电视|网络电视]]剧集《'''[[超感8人组|超感8人组]]'''》的'''第1季'''由[[沃卓斯基姐妹|沃卓斯基姐妹]]和[[约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基|约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基]]创作，关于八名来自世界各地的陌生人突然变得“通感”的故事，或者说他们产生了心理和情感上的联系。本季由沃卓斯基姐妹的Anarchos Productions和斯特拉日恩斯基的{{tsl|en|Studio JMS|JMS工作室}}以及Javelin Productions和Georgeville Television为[[网飞|网飞]]制作。<ref name="Variety">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/reviews/sense8-wachowskis-netflix-review-1201499916/ |title=TV Review: 'Sense8' |author=Brian Lowry |date=2015-05-27 |work=[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] |publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation}} |accessdate=2015-03-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507021859/http://variety.com/2015/tv/reviews/sense8-wachowskis-netflix-review-1201499916/ |archivedate=2016-03-07|deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>Unpronounceable Productions被设立以监督制作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=48623 |title=NYCC: J. Michael Straczynski Opens Up on His Past and Present |author=Meagan Damore |date=2013-10-21 |work={{tsl|en|Comic Book Resources}} |publisher=Valnet |accessdate=2016-05-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507023316/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=48623 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20140731/uptown/netflix-series-sense8-filming-car-chase-crash-buena-park |title=Netflix Series 'Sense8' Filming Car Chase and Crash in Buena Park |author=Adeshina Emmanuel |work={{tsl|en|DNAinfo.com}} |publisher=New Media News |date=2014-07-31 |accessdate=2014-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507023723/https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20140731/uptown/netflix-series-sense8-filming-car-chase-crash-buena-park |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=yes |language=en}}</ref>

该剧负责演绎八名陌生人的多国[[群戏|群演]]包括[[艾繆·艾敏|艾繆·艾敏]]、[[裴斗娜|裴斗娜]]、[[杰米·克莱顿|杰米·克莱顿]]、{{tsl|en|Tina Desai|缇娜·德赛}}、{{tsl|en|Tuppence Middleton|杜蓬斯·米德尔顿}}、[[马克斯·瑞麦尔特|马克斯·瑞麦尔特]]、{{tsl|en|Miguel Ángel Silvestre|米格尔·安吉尔·斯尔文斯特尔}}和[[布莱恩·J·史密斯|布莱恩·J·史密斯]]。[[費馬·阿吉曼|費馬·阿吉曼]]、{{tsl|en|Terrence Mann|特伦斯·曼}}、[[阿努帕姆·卡爾|阿努帕姆·卡爾]]、{{tsl|en|Naveen Andrews|娜文·安德鲁斯}}和[[戴露·漢娜|戴露·漢娜]]亦参与了演出。这一季是计划的5季中的第1季，作为八名通感者的{{tsl|en|origin story|起源故事}}。<ref name="screener">{{cite interview |url=http://screenertv.com/blog-post/netflixs-sense8-details-and-a-new-comic-from-j-michael-straczynski/ |title=Netflix's 'Sense8' details and a new comic from J. Michael Straczynski |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=J. Michael Straczynski |interviewer=Andrea Reiher |date=2014-02-03 |work={{tsl|en|Screener (website)||Screener}} |publisher={{tsl|en|Tribune Media||Tribune Media}} |accessdate=2016-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031120227/http://screenertv.com/blog-post/netflixs-sense8-details-and-a-new-comic-from-j-michael-straczynski/ |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref> 本季剧本由沃卓斯基姐妹和斯特拉日恩斯基撰写，并且大多数集由沃卓斯基姐妹亲自执导，其它的分别由她们的[[沃卓斯基姐妹|频繁合作者]]——[[詹姆斯·麦克特格|詹姆斯·麦克特格]]、[[汤姆·提克威尔|汤姆·提克威尔]]和丹·格拉斯执导。<ref name="gamesradar">{{cite interview |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/first-trailer-wachowskis-sense8-released/ |title=First Trailer For The Wachowskis' Sense8 Released |subject=Grant Hill |subjectlink=Grant Hill (producer) |interviewer=Jordan Farley |date=2015-05-07 |work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |accessdate=2015-05-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507024403/http://www.gamesradar.com/first-trailer-wachowskis-sense8-released/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref> 拍摄基本上完全是在世界各地的各个城市[[外景拍摄|取外景]]，包括[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]、[[旧金山|旧金山]]、[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[柏林|柏林]]、[[首爾|首爾]]、[[雷克雅維克|雷克雅維克]]、[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]、[[奈洛比|奈洛比]]和[[孟买|孟买]]。<ref name="Deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/netflix-wachowski-series-sense8-cast-naveen-andrews-darryl-hannah/ |title=Cast Set, Plot Revealed For Wachowskis' Netflix Globe-Spanning Series 'Sense8' |author=Nellie Andreeva |date=2014-06-20 |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation||Penske Media Corporation}} |accessdate=2014-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507131531/http://deadline.com/2014/06/netflix-wachowski-series-sense8-cast-naveen-andrews-darryl-hannah-794011/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>

本季的全部12集于2015年6月5日在[[流媒体|流媒体]]服务网站网飞上首发，赢得评论界的几乎一致好评。它因其中[[LGBT|LGBT]]角色的演出和主题而著称，并赢得了[[GLAAD媒体奖|GLAAD媒体奖]]杰出剧情类剧集奖。 它亦获得了{{tsl|en|Location Managers Guild Awards|外景制片人协会奖}}对其将外景用作故事中不可或缺的一部分的手法的认可，以及[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]的{{tsl|en|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Main Title Theme Music||杰出原创主题曲奖}}的提名。当年8月8日，网飞宣布续订第2季。<ref>{{Cite tweet |number=630030865054109698 |user=netflix |title=Birthdays are just the beginning. #sense8 is reborn. |date=2015-08-08 |author=网飞 |authorlink=网飞 |accessdate=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509122847/https://twitter.com/netflix/status/630030865054109698 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>{{TOC limit|3}}

