== 反响 ==

=== 评论与流行 ===
《超感8人组》第1季的评论界反馈总体正面。{{tsl|en|review aggregator||评论收集}}网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]给出了67%的新鲜度和基于43次评分给出的6.11/10平均分。 评论的共识是：“部分剧情接近不合逻辑的边缘，但是多样立体的角色和不同故事线间的有趣交集仍然使这部剧集引人注目。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/sense8/s01/ |title=Sense8: Season 1 (2015) |work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] --> |accessdate=2017-01-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106191756/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/sense8/s01/ |archivedate=2017-01-06 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，基于23个评论的[[加權平均數|加权平均分]]为63/100，是“一般性的正面评价”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/sense8 |title=Sense8 : Season 1 |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2015-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507134404/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/sense8 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>

在网飞的一份报告中，70%至少看到了第3集的观众看完了整个第1季，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/netflix-tv-show-data-viewer-episode-study-1201600746/ |title=Netflix Data Reveals Exactly When TV Shows Hook Viewers — And It's Not the Pilot |author=Todd Spangler |date=2015-09-23 |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|}}|accessdate=2015-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507134553/http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/netflix-tv-show-data-viewer-episode-study-1201600746/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>斯特拉日恩斯基被告知有人“反复看完了三四次，甚至六次”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/sdcc-jms-announces-flash-earth-one-talks-gender-issues-on-television |title=SDCC: JMS Announces "Flash: Earth One," Talks "Sense8" Renewal Hopes |author=Seth Rosenblatt |date=2015-07-12 |work={{tsl|en|Comic Book Resources|}}|publisher=Valnet |accessdate=2015-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507134858/http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/sdcc-jms-announces-flash-earth-one-talks-gender-issues-on-television |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>在网飞的另一份报告中，《超感8人组》被列为人们更愿意一次性看完而非断续看完的那类剧集之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-binge-new-binge-scale-reveals-tv-series-we-devour-and-those-we-savor-1 |title=Netflix & Binge: New Binge Scale Reveals TV Series We Devour and Those We Savor |work=[[网飞|网飞]] |date=2016-06-08 |accessdate=2016-06-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608200646/https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-binge-new-binge-scale-reveals-tv-series-we-devour-and-those-we-savor-1 |archivedate=2016-06-08 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>网飞的首席内容官{{tsl|en|Ted Sarandos|泰德·萨兰多斯}}盛赞了《超感8人组》在其新兴的法国和德国市场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/netflixs-ted-sarandos-schmoozes-with-italian-industry-at-ischia-global-fest-1201542936/ |title=Netflix's Ted Sarandos Schmoozes With Italian Industry At Ischia Global Fest |author=Nick Vivarelli |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|}}|accessdate=2015-07-17 |date=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507135027/http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/netflixs-ted-sarandos-schmoozes-with-italian-industry-at-ischia-global-fest-1201542936/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>乃至全球的成功。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/netflix-content-spending-increase-subscriptions-1201476502/ |title=Netflix Execs Say Programming Outlays Will Open Global Doors, And Wallets |author=David Lieberman |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|}}|date=2015-07-15 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507135222/http://deadline.com/2015/07/netflix-content-spending-increase-subscriptions-1201476502/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>掌管国际剧集业务的网飞副总裁埃里克·巴尔麦克称《超感8人组》是网飞在巴西市场最成功的剧集之一。<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/ilustrada/2016/12/1842940-embalada-pela-netflix-assinatura-de-servico-de-streaming-dobra-no-brasil.shtml |title=Embalada pela Netflix, assinatura de serviço de streaming dobra no Brasil |subject=Erik Barmack |interviewer=Nelson de Sá |date=2016-12-20 |work=[[聖保羅頁報|Folha de S.Paulo]] |accessdate=2016-12-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161224202902/http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/ilustrada/2016/12/1842940-embalada-pela-netflix-assinatura-de-servico-de-streaming-dobra-no-brasil.shtml |archivedate=2016-12-24 |deadurl=no |language=pt-br}} </ref>第1季首映不到三天，《综艺》杂志就报道它已经被[[盗版|盗版]]超过五十万次，绕过了剧集的数字分发系统。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/digital/news/netflix-sense8-piracy-wachowskis-1201514526/ |title=Netflix 'Sense8' Thriller from Wachowskis Pirated More Than 500,000 Times Since Debut |author=Todd Spangler |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Penske Media Corporation|}}|accessdate=2015-06-12 |date=2015-06-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/201605071